    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Uchiha Clan, Level 4+</p><p>You've trained yourself to constantly evolve past your current limitations, you gain the following benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Increase your Dexterity or Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20. </p><p><br />• You gain an additional adaptation from the Advanced Adaptation clan feature that you qualify for. </p><p><br />• You can create and learn Uchiha clan Hijutsu in half the required time. </p><p><br />• You can take this feat up to three times.</p>",
